"title": "5465: profit",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5465",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>In the financial sense, gain through trading. The word is also used in Scripture of spiritual gain.</p>\n<h2>Legitimate profit</h2>\n<h3>As the result of hard work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:23\">PRO 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:5\">PRO 21:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:18\">PRO 31:18</a></p>\n<h3>As the reward of generosity</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:24\">PRO 11:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:38\">LUK 6:38</a></p>\n<h3>As the gift of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a></p>\n<h3>It is withheld by God in judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15-Deut28:20\">DEU 28:15–28:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:13\">JER 12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:9\">HAG 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>It is for this life only</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:3-Eccl1:4\">ECC 1:3–1:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:7\">1TI 6:7</a></p>\n<h2>Profiting by oppression</h2>\n<h3>A common practice of the wicked</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:8-Eccl5:9\">ECC 5:8–5:9</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It is often cloaked in hypocrisy</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a></p>\n<h3>It is against God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:37\">LEV 25:37</a></strong></p>\n<h3>It is of little worth</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:16\">PRO 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:8\">PRO 16:8</a></p>\n<h3>It is short-lived</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:18-Job20:19\">JOB 20:18–20:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa23:17-Isa23:18\">ISA 23:17–23:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a></p>\n<h3>It is judged by God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:18-Prov1:19\">PRO 1:18–1:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:12-Ezek22:14\">EZK 22:12–22:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:13\">MIC 4:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:9\">HAB 2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Its avoidance is rewarded</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:16\">PRO 28:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:15-Isa33:16\">ISA 33:15–33:16</a></p>\n<h2>Profiting by dishonesty</h2>\n<h3>It is common amongst the wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:17\">JER 22:17</a></p>\n<h3>It is forbidden to God's servants</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:21\">EXO 18:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:3\">1SA 8:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:8\">1TI 3:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:7\">TIT 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Profiting selfishly</h2>\n<h3>It is common amongst the wicked</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:11\">ISA 56:11</a></p>\n<h3>It is avoided by the godly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:36\">PSA 119:36</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Using religion for profit</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:16-Num22:17\">NUM 22:16–22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:12-1Sam2:16\">1SA 2:12–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13\">JER 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:10\">JER 8:10</a></p>\n<h3>In the NT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:18-Acts8:23\">ACT 8:18–8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:5\">1TI 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:11\">TIT 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:11\">JUD 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Profiting spiritually</h2>\n<h3>Through the Scriptures</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13-1Tim4:15\">1TI 4:13–4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:14\">PRO 3:13–3:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Through doctrine</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:8\">TIT 3:8</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Through godliness and contentment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6\">1TI 6:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Through chastening</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>Through spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:7\">1CO 12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Through service</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:14-Matt25:30\">MAT 25:14–25:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:11-Luke19:27\">LUK 19:11–19:27</a></p>\n<h3>Through sacrifice</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:29\">MAT 19:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:29-Mark10:30\">MRK 10:29–10:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:29-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:29–18:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35\">HEB 11:35</a></p>\n<h3>Through death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:21\">PHP 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23\">PHP 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Doubts expressed about profiting spiritually</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:29-Job9:31\">JOB 9:29–9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:15\">JOB 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:9\">JOB 34:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job35:1-Job35:3\">JOB 35:1–35:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13\">PSA 73:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:15\">ECC 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:8\">ECC 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14\">MAL 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>It is better than worldly wealth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:36\">MRK 8:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a></p>\n<h2>Unprofitable things</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:11\">ECC 6:11</a> <em>mere words</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:11\">ECC 10:11</a> <em>delayed action</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:10\">ISA 44:10</a> <em>idolatry</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:7\">PHP 3:7</a> <em>legalistic works</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1-1Cor13:3\">1CO 13:1–13:3</a> <em>zeal without love</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:6\">1CO 14:6</a> <em>speech without understanding</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:2\">HEB 4:2</a> <em>hearing without faith</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9\">TIT 3:9</a> <em>needless controversy</em></p>",
